<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="8Sep1936"><font color="red">8 September 1936</font> <i>NLPL</i> (to Paul L&eacute;on): <i>Ulysses</i>: Is this to appear in London on Friday 25? &hellip; Any proof which reaches me between date of your departure and Monday 14 will be sent by me by air mail to London within an hour of their receipt. I hoped Wegner could receive them. Rang up. He is away but expected back today &hellip; Please forward a few <i>Irish Times</i> (Saturdays and Fridays preferred). </div>
